        "content": "<p>What's the best way in a linux/mac shell script to detect if sushi detects errors? the 'special' variable '$?' doesn't seem to be set...</p>",
        "id": 204247218,
        "sender_full_name": "David Hay",
        "timestamp": 1595013304
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>By request of the Sushi dev team, I use the exit code</p>",
        "id": 204411702,
        "sender_full_name": "Grahame Grieve",
        "timestamp": 1595245052
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"191321\">@David Hay</span> -- it is working for me on Mac OS X.</p>\n<p>Success:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>╔════════════════════════ SUSHI RESULTS ══════════════════════════╗\n║ ╭──────────┬────────────┬───────────┬─────────────┬───────────╮ ║\n║ │ Profiles │ Extensions │ ValueSets │ CodeSystems │ Instances │ ║\n║ ├──────────┼────────────┼───────────┼─────────────┼───────────┤ ║\n║ │    9     │     6      │     2     │      4      │     5     │ ║\n║ ╰──────────┴────────────┴───────────┴─────────────┴───────────╯ ║\n║                                                                 ║\n║ See SUSHI-GENERATED-FILES.md for details on generated IG files. ║\n╠═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣\n║ Cool and So-fish-ticated!              0 Errors      0 Warnings ║\n╚═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n$ echo $?\n0\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n<p>Error:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>╔════════════════════════ SUSHI RESULTS ══════════════════════════╗\n║ ╭──────────┬────────────┬───────────┬─────────────┬───────────╮ ║\n║ │ Profiles │ Extensions │ ValueSets │ CodeSystems │ Instances │ ║\n║ ├──────────┼────────────┼───────────┼─────────────┼───────────┤ ║\n║ │    9     │     6      │     2     │      4      │     5     │ ║\n║ ╰──────────┴────────────┴───────────┴─────────────┴───────────╯ ║\n║                                                                 ║\n║ See SUSHI-GENERATED-FILES.md for details on generated IG files. ║\n╠═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╣\n║ That really smelt.                      1 Error      0 Warnings ║\n╚═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\n$ echo $?\n1\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 204427979,
        "sender_full_name": "Chris Moesel",
        "timestamp": 1595254907
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"191469\">@Chris Moesel</span> not really related to David's question - if there are warnings, what is the exit code?</p>",
        "id": 204433302,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1595257278
